Absolutely wonderful side dish! A couple modifications were needed, however as others suggested. More maple syrup and more salt. I have made this twice, both with about 2lbs of potatoes and used more than 2 tbl of maple syrup both times. Also, continue to salt to taste b/c the salt is what balances the maple and makes this better than a candied potato dish. Oh, and less butter.

