Rating: 3
I want to say that I love the recipe and I think that basically it is ok. Just a few tips. Do NOT puree this! It will come out like baby food. You want the tartness of some lumps of potato and the sweetness of the smoother parts. Also, ease up on the cream and use salted butter. This takes a LOT of salt to make it just right, and the salted butter helps with that. Other than those tips this is a good recipe.

